. It shall be most holy for you. </span><span class=\"v1_30_37\"><sup id=\"Exod.30.37\" class=\"v1_30_37\">37</sup>And the incense that you shall make according to its composition, you shall not make for yourselves. It shall be for you holy to the <span class=\"nd\">Lord</span>. </span><span class=\"v1_30_38\"><sup id=\"Exod.30.38\" class=\"v1_30_38\">38</sup>Whoever makes any like it to use as perfume shall be cut off from his people.\u201d</span></p>\n</div>\n", 
